items.title: Railway secures $100 million to challenge AWS with AI-native cloud infrastructure
items.summary: San Francisco-based cloud platform has quietly amassed two million developers without spending a dollar on marketing . The investment values Railway as one of the most significant infrastructure startups to emerge during the AI boom . The company processes more than 10 million deployments monthly and handles over one trillion requests through its edge network . Customers report a tenfold increase in developer velocity and up to 65 percent cost savings compared to traditional cloud providers .
